# Build the Reactions Bridge

## Step

Resolved when a reaction (or short reply) on an outbound message
reaches the owning consumer as an event with the original message's
correlation id — and the first customer works end to end: reacting to
a neat-memory DM writes the `outcome` grade into
`~/.joelclaw/observer-neat-memories.json`, feeding the
[reactions-teach-taste loop](../recall-consumption/build-neat-memory-dm.svx).
